Title: Part 15: Destroy The One Ring!
Text:
One Ring to rule them all!
to find them all
to drift into the dark.
And bind forever!

Throw the one ring of power
into the lava of Mount Doom!
And saves the whole of Middle-earth from destruction!
CompleteText:
Here it is... the place where Sauron once forged the one ring of power!

..the only place where he can be destroyed!

<You lean over the slope and take the ring out of your pocket...>

The fate of all Middle-earth depends on this moment!

The story ends here! Well done! @p you will be sung about in songs!

An eagle awaits you on the road to the east!
